pan class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">ij</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.03588em;">v</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.3117em;"><span style="top:-2.55em;margin-left:-0.0359em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathnormal mtight" style="margin-right:0.05724em;">j</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.2861em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<h1 id="transformers" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#transformers"><span>Transformers</span></a></h1>
<p>Self-attention에 기반한 neural networks</p>
<h2 id="transformer" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#transformer"><span>Transformer</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>오직 Attention Mechanism만으로 설계된 Neural Architecture (CNN이나 RNN 미사용)
<ul>
<li>&quot;Attention is all you need&quot; (Ashish Vaswani et al., NeurIPS 2017)</li>
<li>핵심 요소인 Self-Attention Mechanism</li>
<li>Representation의 병렬 계산 가능 및 Scalability 향상</li>
<li>본래 Machine Translation (Seq2seq Architecture)을 위해 제안됨</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="@source/ai/image-92.png" alt=""></p>
<p><img src="@source/ai/image-93.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="the-transformer-decoder" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#the-transformer-decoder"><span>The Transformer Decoder</span></a></h2>
<ul>
<li>Language Model과 같은 시스템 구축에 활용되는 Transformer Decoder
<ul>
<li>최소한의 Self-Attention Architecture와 유사하나 몇 가지 추가 구성 요소 포함</li>
<li>Embedding과 Position Embedding은 동일</li>
<li>기존 Self-Attention을 Multi-Head Self-Attention으로 대체</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="@source/ai/image-94.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="recall-the-self-attention-hypothetical-example" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#recall-the-self-attention-hypothetical-example"><span>Recall the Self-Attention Hypothetical Example</span></a></h2>
<p><img src="@source/ai/image-95.png" alt=""></p>
<h2 id="hypothetical-example-of-multi-head-attention" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#hypothetical-example-of-multi-head-attention"><span>Hypothetical Example of Multi-Head Attention</span></a></h2>
